original_title: Honningsvågrevyen: Det e No Det Gjeld
overview: In this show you'll meet characters like daddy's boy Fillip from Bø, Finn Arild Selnes as the well-spoken lapp and many more familiar faces. We'll also get to know Arnt Hjalmar - leader of the local Amcar club. Arnt Hjalmar is portayed by Stein Arild Olaussen, one of the two new members of the cast. Securitas, the royal family, urban women, old home patients, Ozzy Osbourne, priests... Honningsvågrevyen will make fun of everything.
tagline: Recommended by the bookstore owner in Kabelvåg
title: Honningsvågrevyen: Det e No Det Gjeld
